<step><![CDATA[sprinkle salt on shrimps and stand 10 m (2) make batter by beating eggs well then adding starch (3) dip shrimps in batter and deep fry]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
remove oil, wipe wok, return 1 tbsp of oil in it. very hot (5) stir fry garlic and chili 20s (6) add rice wine, sugar, soy sauce, reduce 40 s (7) add cornstarch mix, 90 s (8) salt to taste and cooked shrimps]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
serve with chili oil and chopped spring onion greens
]]></step>
